Invocation Name: marketing podcast
des:
Insights and tips on the latest in marketing, business, and technology with Emily Binder. Listen to grow your brand or your brain. Answering to no one, always raw. Start the clock on your beetle moment... now!

Emily Binder has a decade of experience in marketing, from startups to global brands. She is a consultant and marketing strategist who specializes in voice search and social media. Beetle Moment is a short weekly podcast hosted by Emily. Available on iTunes, Stitcher, and Amazon Alexa Skills.
